## Attribution Requirements

When sharing or referencing any content from this project, you MUST:

1. **Credit the Author**
   - Include: "Created by Basiliso Rosario"
   - Link to: https://basiliso-rosario.com
   - Or link to: https://linkedin.com/in/basiliso-rosario

2. **Visible Attribution**
   - Attribution must be reasonably visible and not hidden
   - For websites: include in footer, about page, or credits section
   - For presentations: include on a credits slide
   - For documents: include in references or acknowledgments

