## Educational Use Guidelines

This project is provided as a **learning resource**. You are encouraged to study
the code, frameworks, and methodologies to further your understanding of AI,
prompt engineering, and web development.

**You MAY:**
- View and study the source code for personal learning
- Reference the prompt engineering methodologies in your own words
- Share the project link with others (with attribution)
- Use the live site as a learning tool

**You MAY NOT (without written permission):**
- Copy, adapt, or redistribute the code in any project
- Use the code as a template for your own website or application
- Modify and distribute derivative works
- Use for commercial purposes (selling, monetizing, business use)
- Use in paid training materials or courses
- Include in products or services sold to others
- Remove or obscure attribution notices
- Claim the work as entirely your own creation

